data.description: Cozy and well-maintained ranch 3 bedrooms 2 full bathrooms at the well-established Ponderosa Neighborhood. House features tile and hardwood flooring, spacious kitchen, large fence backyard and patio for your enjoyment and outside storages. Replaced roof in 2018, windows in 2019, and water heater 2023. Location, Location! A few minutes away from Fort Liberty, near shopping and restaurants, schedule your showing today!
